NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::ReadmeFromPod - Automatically convert POD to a
    README for Dist::Zilla

VERSION
    version 0.06

SYNOPSIS
        # dist.ini
        [ReadmeFromPod]

        # or
        [ReadmeFromPod]
        filename = lib/XXX.pod

        # to fix "[DZ] attempt to add README multiple times; added by: @Filter/Readme
        [@Filter]
        remove = Readme

        [ReadmeFromPod]

DESCRIPTION
    generate the README from "main_module" (or specified) by Pod::Text

    The code is mostly a copy-paste of Module::Install::ReadmeFromPod

